ess 可以在 Markdown 文件中嵌套 HTML 和 VueJS 代码，然而贴到掘金之后需要我手动贴图，太麻烦了。",{"type":167,"tag":176,"props":182,"children":183},{},[184],{"type":173,"value":185},"于是我测试了几种 Inline CSS 的方案：",{"type":167,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":189},"ul",{},[190,203],{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":192,"children":193},"li",{},[194],{"type":167,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":200},"a",{"href":197,"rel":198},"https://mdnice.com/",[199],"nofollow",[201],{"type":173,"value":202},"MarkdownNice",{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":204,"children":205},{},[206],{"type":167,"tag":195,"props":207,"children":210},{"href":208,"rel":209},"https://github.com/jonkemp/inline-css",[199],[211],{"type":173,"value":212},"InlineCSS",{"type":167,"tag":176,"props":214,"children":215},{},[216],{"type":173,"value":217},"不过结果都不理想，MarkdownNice 的主题，一点儿也不好康。.. InlineCSS 有很多很多很多问题。..",{"type":167,"tag":176,"props":219,"children":220},{},[221],{"type":173,"value":222},"这两种工具我都放弃了，然后我尝试了组合工具的可能性。",{"type":167,"tag":187,"props":224,"children":225},{},[226,231],{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":227,"children":228},{},[229],{"type":173,"value":230},"先通过 SingleFile 将网页保存为一个整体的 HTML 文件",{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":232,"children":233},{},[234],{"type":173,"value":235},"再使用 InlineCSS + Cheerio 手写代码并规避 InlineCSS 的一些配置问题",{"type":167,"tag":176,"props":237,"children":238},{},[239],{"type":173,"value":240},"虽然期间有很多坑，但从最后尝试的结果来说，总的方向可行。",{"type":167,"tag":187,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244,249,254],{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247],{"type":173,"value":248},"SingleFile 会自动内联图片和字体文件，这个好解决，处理之前直接打开控制台修改对应元素避免内联即可，比如将图片的 SRC 属性名改为 SRCBACKUP",{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":250,"children":251},{},[252],{"type":173,"value":253},"InlineCSS 合并时 Margin、MarginBottom 这些重复的属性不会被合并，所以出现了部分样式问题",{"type":167,"tag":191,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257],{"type":173,"value":258},"InlineCSS 解析 CSS 不能解析 CSS 变量",{"type":167,"tag":176,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262],{"type":173,"value":263},"因为相关问题很多，虽然方向可行，但还是弃坑了。最近需要贴文章时还是直接贴 Markdown，懒得再做转换了。以后重新再捡起来的时候，也许会写个直接在浏览器中跑的脚本，毕竟直接调用 DOM API 获取样式的稳定性感觉要比用 InlineCSS 好。",{"title":160,"searchDepth":265,"depth":265,"links":266},2,[],"markdown","content:6.maps:_markdown:markdown.md","content","6.maps/_markdown/markdown.md","6.maps/_markdown/markdown","md",[274,278],{"_path":275,"title":276,"description":277},"/maps/_management/shape-up","Shape Up","适合中小团队的一种工作方式。",{"_path":279,"title":280,"description":281},"/maps/_medicine/medicine","医疗","常见医疗知识、疾病、药物等。",1742348684413]